  "decision_conditions": [
    "FORMAL DECISION\r\n\r\nI allow the appeal and grant planning permission for a bay window extension to kitchen to rear at upper ground floor level with ancillary improvements to the fenestration of the adjoining window, decking and staircase at 15 Richmond Crescent, London, N1 0LZ in accordance with the terms of the application [Ref: P031331) dated 18th June 2003 and the plans submitted therewith, subject to the following conditions:\r\n\r\n1)  The development hereby permitted shall be begun before the expiration of five years from the date of this decision.\r\n\r\n2)  No development shall take place until details of the external joinery and samples of all external materials including a brick and mortar panel demonstrating the proposed bond, have been submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority.  Development shall be carried out in accordance with the approved details."
